NOTICE REGARDING USPS DATA:
This library facilitates access to the United States Postal Service (USPS) Every Door Direct Mail (EDDM) API, available at https://gis.usps.com/. Data retrieved from the USPS EDDM API, including carrier route polygons, ZIP/CRID mappings, and related information, is owned by the USPS and subject to their Terms of Use (see https://www.usps.com/business/every-door-direct-mail.htm). Users of this library are responsible for complying with USPS terms, including restrictions on commercial redistribution of raw data. This library processes and transforms USPS data for use in EDDM-related applications, such as route selection and analytics, but does not grant any rights to the data itself.
